  "description": "Grafana Faro RUM for the browser app (service.name / app.name = browser). Select your LGTM Loki and Tempo datasources on import. Log panels use {service_name=\"browser\"} (OTLP → Loki). If a panel is empty, open Explore on the same stream and adjust parsers to match your log line format.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "**Faro → Alloy → OTLP → LGTM.** Stream selector: `{service_name=\"browser\"}` (from OTel `service.name`).\n\n- **Page loads** counts log lines that look like view / session / navigation signals (regex over the raw line).\n- **Exceptions** matches `kind=exception`, JSON `\"kind\":\"exception\"`, or common error wording.\n- **Browsers / users** use regexp extractors; if your lines are pure JSON, try the same queries in Explore with `| json` and promote fields via Loki config or duplicate panels with `| json`.\n- **Tempo** panels filter `resource.service.name = \"browser\"`. TraceQL metrics (`| rate()`) need Grafana 10.4+ and TraceQL metrics enabled on Tempo.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Notes",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 100,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Overview (Loki)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "percentChangeColorMode": "standard",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"browser\"} |~ \"(?i)(kind[=:]view|view_changed|session_start|navigation|web-vitals|document.load|pageview)\" [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Total page / view signals",
      "type": "stat"
    },
